    public static final class ForwardingTypes.ConnectionStatus.State
extends ApiEnumeration<ForwardingTypes.ConnectionStatus.State>
    The State enumeration class defines the state values that a remote logging server can be in. This enumeration was added in vSphere API 6.7.

    See enumerated types description.
